"Stop this foolish battle" Megatron yelled, his cannon still smoking from
the outburst of energy. Then over his comm-link he contacted Autofire,
"Autofire, return to base for your briefing," He then contacted Decapitron,
"Decapitron you are relieved of your duty, come up to the surface for your
briefing" he then looked at Drag Strip, Speedbreaker, and Dead-End. You
Stunticons will be left here with Beastbox, Squawktalk and Skullgrin to
guard. Triggerhappy, you and Fireblade will join Autofire the Terrorcons
and Bodicons on this mission".
